# Tech Stack

This project uses the following technologies:

## Framework & Frontend
- **TanStack Start** - React meta-framework with SSR support
- **TanStack Router** - Type-safe file-based routing
- **React 19** - UI library
- **Vite 7** - Build tool and dev server

## Backend & Database
- **Convex** - Real-time serverless backend and database
- **Better Auth** - Authentication library integrated with Convex via `@convex-dev/better-auth`

## Styling & UI
- **Tailwind CSS 4** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **shadcn/ui** - Component library (install via `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>`)
- **Lucide React** - Icon library

## Package Manager & Tooling
- **Bun** - Package manager and runtime
- **TypeScript** - Type-safe JavaScript
- **ESLint** - Linting
- **Prettier** - Code formatting
- **Vitest** - Testing framework

## Project Structure
- `src/routes/` - TanStack Router file-based routes
- `src/components/` - React components
- `src/lib/` - Utility functions and auth configuration
- `convex/` - Convex backend functions and schema
